---
// Header redesigned as a Profile section for the Landing Portal
---

<header class="flex flex-col items-center pt-16 pb-10 text-center">
	<div class="mb-4 relative group">
		<div class="absolute -inset-1 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-blue-600/20 to-sky-400/20 blur opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
		<div
			class="relative flex h-24 w-24 overflow-hidden items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white border border-neutral-200/80 shadow-md ring-8 ring-neutral-50/50"
		>
			<img src="/apple-touch-icon.png" alt="소셜아카이브 로고" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
		</div>
	</div>

	<h1 class="text-2xl font-black tracking-tight text-neutral-900">
		소셜아카이브
	</h1>
</header>
